data.description: Check out this nice brick home in Ridge Hill Trails with a lot of space for a growing family. This split foyer plan offers 3 bedrooms and 2 baths on main level. Kitchen and dining combo with breakfast bar and dining area which opens to a great room. Outside composite deck for grilling over looking the large backyard. It has a huge primary bedroom and bathroom on one side of great room along with 2 bedrooms and a bathroom on the other. Basement level is partly finished with a spacious family room and bedroom.  New to the market so call today and check this out now.
